<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="https://www.thymeleaf.org">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>DGRMagicNumber</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        
</head>
<body class= "bg-dark">
    <div class= "container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-5 mt-3">
        <img src="{{ asset('images/logo.jpeg') }}" alt="logo">
         <h1 class="text-center mb-5"><a class="text-decoration-none text-warning" href="{{ path('index') }}">{{ appName }}</a></h1>
    </div>  
      
    <div class="container mt-5 text-white">

        <h1 class="text-center">Palabra Mágica</h1>
        <p class="text-center mt-3">
            El número mágico <strong class= "display-6">{{ magicNumber }}</strong> está asociado a la palabra mágica: <strong class= "display-5 text-primary">{{ magicWord }}</strong>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-center mt-3">
            Esta palabra te traerá mucha suerte. ¿Quieres conocer su significado?
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ path('dictionary', {'word': magicWord}) }}">Haz clic aquí <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-arrow-right"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></a>
        </p>
        <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <a href="{{ path('magic_number') }}" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Escoger otro número mágico</a>

    </div>
</body>

<script th:href="@{/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js}"></script>

</html>